Game Design Document

Bottom line: You can have it all, but not all at the same time

Gist: to demonstrate competing activities at HBS with limited time and energy.

MATH
	[time]
	Assumes that everyone goes to school from 9am - 3pm (6 hours).
	Total time to allocate every day is 18 hours (24 hours - 6 hours).
	Default 8 hours of sleep. 
	Free time to read cases or parties: 10 hours (18-8 hours).
	Each case takes 3 hours to prep.
	Each party takes 10 hours.
